This paper involves the study of Bitcoin donations to open source repositories on GitHub, which falls under the category of cybernetics (cs.CY). It also involves the analysis of transactions from Bitcoin's public blockchain, which falls under the category of cryptography (cs.CR). Additionally, the paper involves the study of software development and version control, which falls under the categories of software engineering (cs.SE) and social and information networks (cs.SI). Finally, the paper involves the analysis of correlations between variables, which falls under the category of systems and control (cs.SY).
